BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Q4ps-Bxw2v0W8CTDRArch
SUMMARY:Hiking Club to Mount Si 🌹
DTSTAMP:20260413T005356Z
DTSTART:20260503T080000Z
DESCRIPTION:We’re socialists who hike! \\nMay we’ll be hiking Mount Si (8.0
	 miles) in the North Bend area. Let’s enjoy some early season hiking. DSA 
	membership not required. \\nMeet in the Hilltop Red Apple parking lot. Sna
	cks and transportation to the trail provided. \\nRecommended pack list:\\n
	* Hiking boots\\n* Water\\n* Lunch or snacks\\n* Jacket\\n* Map (Apple or 
	Google offline download\\\, AllTrails)\\n* Sunglasses (weather depending)\
	\n* Rain coat (weather depending)\\n* Phone battery pack (optional)\\nSee 
	REI day hiking checklist for additional recommendations\n\nhttps://seattle
	dsa.org/event/hiking-club-to-mount-si-%f0%9f%8c%b9/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/hiking-club-to-mount-si-%f0%9f%8c%b9/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:GvC3fvI_a6LyMCdYn0fyM
SUMMARY:Socialist Soccer! - 10am to 12pm
DTSTAMP:20260413T005356Z
DTSTART:20260503T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come play soccer with fellow socialists! This is a fun\\\, enjo
	yable way to get outdoors\\\, exercise\\\, and meet friendly socialists as
	 well as non-socialist soccer enthusiasts! \\nAll genders and skill levels
	 are welcome! Safety is our top priority. To participate you must abide by
	 our norms and agreements to avoid injuries and help us take care of one a
	nother. \\nJoin us at Brighton Playfield in South Seattle. Map: goo.gl/map
	s/c74cytjrRB1vpT7h7\\nWe almost always play on the most southern edge of t
	he field. \\nWe confirm if we have enough players each Sunday on a sociali
	st soccer Signal chat. To be added\\\, download the Signal app\\\, and ema
	il your phone number to tdupuis42@gmail.com with a request to be added. \\
	nThe game is usually at 10 AM\\\, but that may change\\\, so make sure you
	 are on the Socialist Soccer signal chat!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/
	socialist-soccer-10am-to-12pm/2026-05-03/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-soccer-10am-to-12pm/2026-05-03/
LOCATION:Brighton Playfield\\\, 6000 39th Ave S\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 9811
	8\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
