BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8scuFivuoLbuI76eZOHez
SUMMARY:Local Council Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260413T005356Z
DTSTART:20260519T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Local Council (LC) is the elected leadership body which ser
	ves the members of Seattle DSA. During these short weekly check-ins\\\, LC
	 members will primarily be ensuring work is on track\\\, though pressing b
	usiness may occasionally be discussed and voted on. Members are welcome to
	 observe LC meetings\\\, which are held on the chapter’s Discord server. T
	o join our Discord\\\, please visit https://seattledsa.org/join-discord/ a
	nd follow the instructions. Thereafter\\\, you will be able to observe LC 
	meetings on the #lc-voice channel every Tuesday (except the fourth Tuesday
	 of the month when we hold our monthly General Membership Meeting) from 7:
	00pm – 7:45pm over Zoom. \\nIf there’s something specific you’d like to br
	ing to the Local Council\\\, please fill out the LC Request Form which can
	 be found on the private resources page of our website. \\nPlease note tha
	t on rare occurrences\\\, LC meetings will be cancelled due to holidays or
	 unusual circumstances and these changes may not always be reflected on th
	is calendar — if you show up to the meeting and aren’t let in after 5 minu
	tes\\\, that is almost certainly what has happened.\n\nhttps://seattledsa.
	org/event/local-council-meeting-6-2-2/2026-05-19/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/local-council-meeting-6-2-2/2026-05-19/
LOCATION:Online (Discord)
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
